title: Ukraine's Poroshenko calls Russian election illegitimate
text:
Ukraine's Poroshenko calls Russian election illegitimate 9:13am EDT - 00:48 
Ukrainian President Petro Poroshekno says Vladimir Putin's re-election was illegitimate, drawing a comparison to what the Poroshenko called the ''null and void'' election in Crimea. Rough cut (no reporter narration).
